# NexoralDNS Core Rules for Cursor IDE

## Project Context

**NexoralDNS** is an Advanced DNS Management & Surveillance System for Local Area Networks (LAN). High-performance DNS server with sub-5ms query response times.

## ⚠️ CRITICAL: LAN-ONLY DEPLOYMENT

**NEVER suggest cloud or public deployment**
- ISPs will block DNS spoofing
- Service will become non-functional on public networks
- This is STRICTLY for Local Area Network use only

## Mandatory Workflows

### After EVERY Code Change
```bash
cd server && npm run build    # Server changes
cd Web && npm run build       # Dashboard changes
cd DHCP && npm run build      # DHCP changes
```

### For ANY Feature Change
1. Update tests in `Test/` directory
2. Run `cd Test && npm test` - all tests must pass
3. Update docs (README.md, ARCHITECTURE.md, FEATURES.md)
4. Verify performance targets (<5ms)

